## CARA KERJA PARALLAX

### scroll-animate.js — engine, TIDAK PERNAH DIUBAH
- Baca `window.scenes` dari `scenes.js`
- Tiap scene = satu halaman scroll (100vh)
- Lookup elemen by `id`, apply transform berdasarkan scroll progress
- Otomatis append `#lastContainer` ke scene terakhir

### scenes.js — BUAT BARU TIAP TEMA
```javascript
window.scenes = [
  {
    smoothingFactor: 0.015, // 0.01 = lambat dreamy, 0.025 = dramatis
    [element_id]: {
      speed: 1,             // >1 = lebih cepat dari scroll
      keyframes: [
        { progress: 0,   x: 0,   y: 0,   scale: 1,   rotate: 0, opacity: 1 },
        { progress: 0.5, x: 100, y: 50,  scale: 1.5, rotate: 0, opacity: 0.5 },
        { progress: 1,   x: 200, y: 200, scale: 2,   rotate: 0, opacity: 0 },
      ]
    },
  },
  // ... total 6 scene
];
```

**Aturan:**
- `progress` 0.0–1.0 per scene
- `x`, `y` = pixel offset dari posisi CSS awal elemen
- scenes.js harus punya **tepat 6 scene** (index 0–5)
- Scene 0 = cover, Scene 1–4 = parallax tengah, Scene 5 = transisi ke lastContainer

### ID elemen WAJIB ada di HTML
```
#mobileContainer, #stage, #scrollContainer, #scrollContent, #lastContainer

Layer parallax (class="animated-element"):
#bg, #arch, #floor, #couple, #tree1, #tree3, #butterfly

Cover (class="animated-element cover"):
#coverOverlay, #coverFlower1, #coverLogo, #coverText, #guest

Dalam cover:
#coverInitialPria, #coverSeparator, #coverInitialWanita
#coverTitle, #coverNames, #coverDate
#coverSalam, #guestGreeting, #guestName
#arrowDown, #coverButton, #coverButtonText

Text scene tengah:
#quotes, #quotesText
#bride: #brideNickname, #brideFullName, #brideProfile
#groom: #groomNickname, #groomFullName, #groomProfile
#events: #eventsSectionTitle, #eventsContainer
#verse: #verseText, #verseSource

Lain:
#mp3-player, #music-button
```

### Posisi layer diatur di CSS (bukan scenes.js)
```css
#bg     { inset: -10% 0; width: 100%; height: 120%; object-fit: cover; }
#arch   { bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
#floor  { bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; }
#couple { bottom: 55px; left: 50%; margin-left: -35%; width: 70%; }
#tree1  { width: 130px; bottom: 240px; right: -15px; }
#tree3  { width: 200px; bottom: 240px; left: -20px; }
```
scenes.js hanya tambah transform di atas posisi CSS ini.

